 } } \right| + \left| {\matrix{
   1 &amp; 0 &amp; 3  \cr 
   3 &amp; 1 &amp; 1  \cr 
   2 &amp; 4 &amp; 5  \cr 

 } } \right|$$<br><br>$$\therefore$$ $$c = ( - 1) + ( - 1)(1 - 6) + 31$$<br><br>$$ =  - 1 + 5 + 31$$<br><br>$$ = 35$$

