Which one of the following factors does the expansion of the determinant <br><br>$$\left| {\matrix{
   x &amp; y &amp; 3  \cr 
   {{x^2}} &amp; {5{y^3}} &amp; 9  \cr 
   {{x^3}} &amp; {10{y^5}} &amp; {27}  \cr 

 } } \right|$$ contain?

explanation:
