 } } \right| = 0$$<br><br>R<sub>1</sub> $$\to$$ R<sub>1</sub> + R<sub>2</sub> + R<sub>3</sub><br><br>$$ \Rightarrow \left| {\matrix{
   {a + b + c - x} &amp; {a + b + c - x} &amp; {a + b + c - x}  \cr 
   c &amp; {b - x} &amp; a  \cr 
   b &amp; a &amp; {c - x}  \cr 

 } } \right| = 0$$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow \left| {\matrix{
   { - x} &amp; { - x} &amp; { - x}  \cr 
   c &amp; {b - x} &amp; a  \cr 
   b &amp; a &amp; {c - x}  \cr 

 } } \right| = 0$$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow ( - x)\left| {\matrix{
   1 &amp; 1 &amp; 1  \cr 
   c &amp; {b - x} &amp; a  \cr 
